N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 9500.11 - Determination and findings

State Regulations

The findings of the commission shall be filed at the place of
business of the St. Lawrence - Eastern Ontario Commission together with all
plans, maps, exhibits and other papers and records relating to the project. These documents may be examined and copies thereof made at the place of
business of the commission during business hours. Notes
